### Base URL (doi port neu can)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ========== AUTH (khong can dang nhap) ==========

### 1. Dang ky user moi
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user3",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ROLE_USER"
}

### 2. Login (admin co san: admin / admin123)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### ========== USER (can Basic Auth) ==========
### Basic = base64(username:password). Admin co san: admin / admin123

### 3. Xem thong tin user hien tai
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### ========== TASKS (user thuong) ==========

### 4. Lay danh sach task cua minh
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### 5. Tao task moi
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

{
  "title": "Hoc Spring Boot",
  "description": "Lam bai tap API"
}

### 6. Xem 1 task theo id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### 7. Cap nhat task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

{
  "title": "Hoc Spring Boot (da xong)",
  "description": "Lam bai tap API"
}

### 8. Xoa task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### ========== ADMIN (chi tai khoan ROLE_ADMIN) ==========

### 9. Lay tat ca user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### 10. Lay 1 user theo id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### 11. Cap nhat user (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

{
  "role": "ROLE_ADMIN",
  "active": true
}

### 12. Lay tat ca task (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tasks
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### 13. Lay task theo userId (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1/tasks
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=
